snippet.title: Strange Terror From The Deep | NEW CHARACTER REVEAL
snippet.description:
Strange Terror From The Deep is getting its entire Deep Terror update I promised a long time ago then shelved due to lack of motivation. After some contemplation (and guilt admittedly, LOL) I've nearly wrapped up the update!

No release date at the moment since I've still got a few things left on my to-do list that I'm not sure how long it'll take to get done. So for now, look forward to it! Hopefully it won't be long...
